{"id":229,"date":"2007-07-05T15:41:40","date_gmt":"2007-07-05T15:41:40","guid":{"rendered":"http://192.168.5.119/2.2/?p=229"},"modified":"2007-07-05T15:41:40","modified_gmt":"2007-07-05T15:41:40","slug":"%e6%94%af%e6%8c%81%e8%b0%8b%e6%99%bamozilla%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c7%e6%9c%88%e6%ad%a3%e5%bc%8f%e6%8c%82%e7%89%8c%e5%b9%b6%e5%be%81%e8%b4%a4%e7%ba%b3%e5%a3%ab","status":"publish","link":"https://xbeta.info/%e6%94%af%e6%8c%81%e8%b0%8b%e6%99%bamozilla%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c7%e6%9c%88%e6%ad%a3%e5%bc%8f%e6%8c%82%e7%89%8c%e5%b9%b6%e5%be%81%e8%b4%a4%e7%ba%b3%e5%a3%ab.htm","title":{"rendered":"支持:谋智(Mozilla)网络7月正式挂牌并征贤纳士"},"content":{"rendered":"<div>　　感谢Mozilla，提供了我每天必用的Firefox、Thunderbird，以及编写网页时应用的Nvu（写源码时直接用VIM）。还有一款Sunbird，我不用，有兴趣者也可一试。以转发广告作为支持。&nbsp;[<a HREF=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/46dac66f010008ck\" TARGET=\"_blank\">网页编辑器，我推荐Nvu</a>] [<a HREF=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/46dac66f01000ak0\" TARGET=\"_blank\">经验：用VIM编写/编辑html</a>]</div>\n<div>　　如下为转发，[<a HREF=\"http://blog.mozilla.com/ligong/2007/06/30/%e8%b0%8b%e6%99%ba%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c7%e6%9c%88%e6%ad%a3%e5%bc%8f%e6%8c%82%e7%89%8c%e5%b9%b6%e5%be%81%e8%b4%a4%e7%ba%b3%e5%a3%ab/\" TARGET=\"_blank\">原文在此</a>]。</div>\n<div>\n<h2><a TITLE=\"Permanent Link: 谋智网络7月正式挂牌并征贤纳士\" HREF=\"http://blog.mozilla.com/ligong/2007/06/30/%e8%b0%8b%e6%99%ba%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c7%e6%9c%88%e6%ad%a3%e5%bc%8f%e6%8c%82%e7%89%8c%e5%b9%b6%e5%be%81%e8%b4%a4%e7%ba%b3%e5%a3%ab/\" REL=\"bookmark\">谋智网络7月正式挂牌并征贤纳士</a></h2>\n<div CLASS=\"entry\">\n<p CLASS=\"MsoPlainText\">\n下周一<span>谋智网络正式挂牌营业。我们的地址是</span></p>\n<p><span>北京谋智网络技术有限公司</span><span><br />\n北京市海淀区中关村东路</span><span>1</span><span>号清华科技园科技大厦</span><span>C</span><span>座</span><span>1701</span><br />\n<span>（邮编</span><span>100084</span><span>）</span></p>\n<p><span>我们目前着重吸引如下几类贤士：</span></p>\n<p>\n1。战略，计划，市场，公关。在市场分析，客户调查，产品定位，品牌管理，市场宣传，公共关系等方面有经验有见解。</p>\n<p>\n2。技术人员。对互联网技术有热情和理解。有建设和运行网站的经验，或有关于浏览器的经验，优先考虑。</p>\n<p>\n3。我们也欢迎在校生来实习。特别欢迎计算机或相关专业，以及商学院的同学。</p>\n<p>\n我们目前组建一个小的核心团队，工作形式和方式灵活，可考虑兼职或非全时的安排。与在华的跨国公司不同的是，我们每一个人都可参与公司各方面的事务与业务，可以直接影响火狐等产品在中国的走向，以及提议和开发崭新一代的互联网技术和产品。一个好主意，几分钟后即可开始实施。</p>\n<p>志同道和者直接给我写邮件吧。——<span>宫力</span></p>\n<p><span><font COLOR=\"#FF0000\">(xb</font><font COLOR=\"#FF0000\">eta：不过作者没留邮件，也没查到。读者若有意，就到原文留言吧）</font></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>></iframe></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>　　感谢Mozilla，提供了我每天必用的Firefox、Thunderbird，以及编写网页时应用的Nvu（ [&hellip;]</p>\n","protected":false},"author":15,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":["旧.网络相关","未分类"],"tags":["all"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/229"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/users/15"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=229"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/229/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=229"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=229"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=229"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]},"wp_type":"post"}